flowchart TD
  T["Tool Intent"] --> C{"action category"}
  C -->|Glob/Grep| R1["R1 search can be automatically released by default"]
  C -->|Read| RR{"read path"}
  RR -->|Project source code| R1
  RR -->|secrets/cross-border| R5["R5 prohibited"]
  C -->|Edit/Write| R2["R2 writes files usually ask or policy allow"]
  C -->|Bash| BR{"Command classification"}
  BR -->|Test/build read-only tendency| R3["R3 execution may allow/ask"]
  BR -->|Delete/Reset/Network/Install| R4["R4 high risk default ask or deny"]
  BR -->|Parse failure/dangerous wrapper| R5

  R1 --> D1["allow"]
  R2 --> D2{"ask/allow"}
  R3 --> D3{"ask/allow/sandbox"}
  R4 --> D4{"ask/deny"}
  R5 --> D5["deny"]

  R5:::hot
  R4:::hot
  D5:::hot

  classDef hot fill:#fff3b0,stroke:#111,stroke-width:2px,color:#111;
